divs: Sighting DetailsI was at my house looking at the moon, so i decided to take a picture of the moon,, then I saw a little weird object, so i look at the picture and i see 3 really small objects located at the bottom of the picture in the left side of the picture. i couldnt explain those 3 objects, they are just unknown...
Summary: I took a picture and then I saw in the picture 3 weird objects can't explain!
